sults-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebasic%20income%20pilot%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20creatives%20nears%20its%20end%20in%20February%2C%20officials%20have%20to%20answer%20a%20simple%20question%3A%20Is%20it%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20four%20months%20to%20go%2C%20they%20say%20the%20answer%20is%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Ireland's%20government%20announced%20its%202026%20budget%2C%20which%20includes%20%26quot%3Ba%20successor%20to%20the%20pilot%20Basic%20Income%20Scheme%20for%20the%20Arts%20to%20begin%20next%20year%26quot%3B%20among%20its%20expenditures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIreland%20is%20just%20one%20of%20many%20places%20experimenting%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-ubi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguaranteed%20basic%20income%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20provide%20recurring%2C%20unrestricted%20payments%20to%20people%20in%20a%20certain%20demographic.%20These%20programs%20differ%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-pros-and-cons%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Euniversal%20basic%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20would%20provide%20payments%20for%20an%20entire%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBasic%20income%20programs%20of%20all%20kinds%20have%20been%20around%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20but%20have%20seen%20renewed%20interest%20since%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20AI%20revolution.%20Some%20of%20the%20world's%20top%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20called%20for%20such%20programs%20to%20alleviate%20the%20loss%20of%20income%20in%20the%20future%20if%20the%20technology%20ousts%20humans%20from%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIreland%20first%20launched%20its%20basic%20income%20pilot%20program%20in%202022%2C%20when%20some%202%2C000%20artists%20began%20receiving%20a%