%20year%2C%20we%20fulfilled%20a%20travel%20pact%20by%20visiting%20Liechtenstein%20together.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20trip%20helped%20us%20reconnect%20and%20appreciate%20our%20differences.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20sister%20and%20I%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsiblings-entrepreneurs-started-business-keys-success-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ealways%20been%20close%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20kind%20of%20way%20that%20only%20siblings%20with%20a%20two-year%20age%20gap%20can%20be.%20We%20grew%20up%20sharing%20everything%20from%20wardrobes%20to%20the%20same%20old%20hand-me-down%20phone.%20As%20adults%2C%20though%2C%20life%20has%20pulled%20us%20in%20different%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%2033%20now%2C%20I'm%2031%2C%20and%20somehow%2C%20we%20spent%20most%20of%20our%20twenties%20living%20in%20different%20countries.%20She%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fsingapore%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Singapore%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20she%20was%2025%2C%20while%20I%20stayed%20in%20India.%20Just%20as%20she%20returned%20home%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-moved-ireland-to-study-never-felt-settled-moved-home-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleft%20for%20Ireland%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20year%20later%20I%20moved%20back%20home%2C%20and%20then%20moved%20again%2C%20this%20time%20to%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20our%20relationship%20existed%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftext-people-too-much-too-quickly-for-validation-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etext%20threads%3C%2Fa%3E%20sent%20from%20different%20time%20zones.%20We%20vicariously%20lived%20through%20each%20other's%20adventures%2C%20always%20promising%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20come%20here%2C%20I'll%20take%20you%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomewhere%20along%20the%20way%2C%20it%20became%20a%20pact%3A%20that%20when%20we%20finally%20got%20the%20chance%2C%20we'd%20travel%20together%20%E2%80%94%20somewhere%20offbeat%2C%20away%20from%20the%20crowds%20and%20big%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c01e8df4-7598-4520-8d82-10e6c50de04b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20finally%20made%20it%20happen%20in%20Liechtenstein%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20December%2C%20our%20calendars%20finally%20aligned%2C%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20visit%20my%20sister%20for%20Christmas.%20It%20felt%20like%20the%20perfect%20time%20to%20honor%20our%20pact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20both%20wanted%20to%20travel%20somewhere%20quiet%2C%20a%20place%20that%20matched%20our%20shared%20introverted%20energy.%20That's%20how%20we%20found%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliechtenstein-map-gdp-per-capita-population-astounding-facts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELiechtenstein%2C%20a%20tiny%20country%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebetween%20Switzerland%20and%20Austria%20that%20looked%20straight%20out%20of%20a%20postcard.%20Neither%20of%20us%20had%20been%20there%20before%2C%20which%20made%20it%20even%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20both%20initially%20wanted%20different%20things%20from%20the%20trip%2C%20which%20became%20clear%20right%20away.%20I'm%20the%20kind%20of%20traveller%20who%20makes%20lists%20of%20places%20to%20see%2C%20things%20to%20eat%2C%20photo%20spots%20%E2%80%94%20all%20mapped%20out%20by%20the%20hour.%20My%20sister%20is%20the%20exact%20opposite.%20She's%20a%20%26quot%3Blet's%20see%20where%20the%20day%20takes%20us%26quot%3B%20kind%20of%20traveller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20we%20had%20a%20few%20disagreements%20about%20where%20to%20start%2C%20but%20since%20this%20trip%20was%20really%20about%20reconnecting%2C%20we%20settled%20on%20three%20spots%20that%20suited%20us%20both%3A%20Vaduz%20Castle%2C%20Stausee%20Steg%20Lake%2C%20and%20Malbun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b86cc3f1-dda4-4575-8024-1824cdfeb34d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20slowed%20down%20just%20enough%20to%20notice%20everything%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliechtenstein-is-beautiful-2015-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVaduz%20Castle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20my%20pick.%20I%20love%20all%20things%20historic%2C%20so%20walking%20up%20the%20hill%20to%20the%20castle%20felt%20like%20stepping%20back%20in%20time.%20We%20kept%20stopping%20to%20read%20the%20little%20signboards%20about%20its%20past%2C%20mostly%20because%20I%20made%20her%2C%20but%20also%20because%20we%20couldn't%20stop%20pausing%20for%20the%20stunning%20views%20of%20the%20Alps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222296%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20sister%20poses%20next%20to%20Lake%20Stausee%20Steg.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f27cb81c1f80efbec5ce4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20says%20that%20visiting%20spots%20like%20Lake%20Stausee%20Steg%20with%20her%20sister%20(shown)%20helped%20them%20reconnect.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Nishtha%20Chaudhary%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lake%2C%20Stausee%20Steg%2C%20was%20my%20sister's%20choice.%20She's%20always%20been%20drawn%20to%20water%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20weather.%20We%20sat%20by%20the%20lake%2C%20eating%20snacks%20we'd%20packed%2C%20and%20talking%20about%20everything%20we'd%20missed%20in%20each%20other's%20lives.%20Seeing%20her%20there%2C%20smiling%20like%20the%20happiest%20kid%20I%20remember%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20we%20could%20finally%20be%20in%20the%20moment%20together%20after%20years%20of%20quick%20catch-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20was%20Malbun%2C%20a%20small%20ski%20village%20tucked%20in%20the%20mountains.%20We%20didn't%20ski%2C%20but%20wandered%20through%20snow-lined%20streets%2C%20sipping%20hot%20chocolate%20and%20taking%20in%20the%20view.%20Being%20there%20felt%20like%20stepping%20into%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-original-christ