ner%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1981%2F10%2F31%2Fnyregion%2Fabout-new-york-belief-in-ghost-haunts-a-historic-mansion.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%201981%20that%20Eliza%20Jumel%20negotiated%20a%20%242%2C000%20discount%20on%20the%20house%20because%20even%20then%20it%20was%20said%20to%20be%20haunted%20by%20the%20ghost%20of%20a%20Hessian%20soldier%20who%20fought%20in%20the%20Revolutionary%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisitors%20and%20employees%20of%20the%20museum%20have%20also%20reported%20incidents%20of%20paranormal%20activity%20since%20it%20opened%20to%20the%20public%20in%201904.%20Some%20tour%20groups%20have%20claimed%20to%20see%20Jumel%C2%A0in%20full%20period%20dress%20on%20the%20second-floor%20balcony.%20Tour%20guides%20say%20they've%20heard%20voices%20and%20footsteps%20with%20no%20one%20else%20present.%20Others%20report%20running%20into%20that%20same%20Hessian%20soldier%20on%20the%20stairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20museum's%20staff%20keeps%20a%20record%20of%20these%20unexplained%20encounters%20known%20as%20the%20Book%20of%20Haunts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20signed%20up%20for%20one%20of%20the%20mansion's%20paranormal-investigation%20tours%20to%20see%20for%20myself.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sign%20advertising%20a%20paranormal%20investigation%20tour%20at%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651434261c099d0019ad2ff8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20sign%20advertising%20a%20paranormal%20investigation%20tour%20at%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20Halloween%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eventbrite.com%2Fo%2Fmorris-jumel-mansion-12776256108%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMorris-Jumel%20Mansion%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20spooky%20tour%20experiences%20in%20addition%20to%20its%20regular%20schedule.%20The%20paranormal%20investigation%20tour%2C%20lasting%202%20%C2%BD%20hours%20and%20featuring%20the%20use%20of%20paranormal%20investigative%20equipment%2C%20costs%20%2465.%20Morris-Jumel%20has%20also%20previously%20conducted%20candlelit%20ghost%20tours%2C%20though%20the%20program%20is%20not%20being%20offered%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMadeline%20Mungo%2C%20the%20mansion's%20public%20programs%20and%20visitor%20services%20manager%2C%20recommended%20that%20I%20book%20the%20paranormal%20investigation%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bmore%20ghostly%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20a%20big%20believer%20in%20ghosts%20and%20paranormal%20activity%2C%20but%20I%20do%20love%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-haunted-roads-ghost-stories-halloween-road-trip-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexploring%20haunted%20places%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20name%20of%20journalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20tour%20began%20with%20an%20introduction%20to%20the%20ghost-hunting%20equipment%20we'd%20be%20using%2C%20such%20as%20REM%20pods.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20paranormal%20research%20instrument.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65143f7aeee46600193b9641%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20paranormal%20research%20instrument.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EREM%20pods%20light%20up%20and%20make%20noise%20when%20they%20detect%20temperature%20shifts%20and%20%26quot%3Bchanges%20of%20the%20surrounding%20energy%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20some%20believe%20are%20indicators%20of%20paranormal%20activity%2C%20according%20to%20the%20device's%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Df75cea4eb82caa71fe28b3a93b300ae9853c859fd96e7df497c301c657da4016%26postID%3D6514337f23b6903d6ac2775f%26postSlug%3Dhaunted-places-historic-homes-to-visit-ghost-tour-2023-9%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FRadiating-Antenna-Paranormal-Hunting-Equipment%252Fdp%252FB01M3N5WT8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0listing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETour%20guide%20Karen%20Compton%20explained%20that%20staff%20would%20bring%20the%20REM%20pod%20from%20room%20to%20room%20as%20our%20tour%20progressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEach%20participant%20also%20received%20an%20electromagnetic%20field%20(EMF)%20meter.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20EMF%20meter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65143c951c099d0019ad3319%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20EMF%20meter.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EElectricians%20use%20EMF%20meters%20to%20diagnose%20electrical%20or%20wiring%20issues.%20Paranormal%20researchers%20use%20them%20to%20measure%20electromagnetic%20energy%20that%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20ghosts%20or%20spirits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Compton%20said%2C%20if%20we%20held%20up%20the%20EMF%20meter%20to%20a%20piece%20of%20wooden%20furniture%20with%20no%20electric%20wiring%20inside%20and%20the%20lights%20flashed%20to%20indicate%20a%20strong%20electromagnetic%20field%2C%20it%20could%20mean%20a%20ghost%20is%20responsible.%20Or%2C%20she%20said%2C%20it%20could%20mean%20that%20we're%20near%20a%20lightbulb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnother%20surprising%20tool%20used%20by%20paranormal%20researchers%3A%20motion-activated%20cat%20ball%20toys.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cat%20balls%20on%20a%20mantle%20at%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65143c921c099d0019ad330d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECat%20balls%20on%20a%20mantle.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cat%20ball%20toys%20light%20up%20when%20something%20touches%20them%20or%20moves%20near%20them.%20If%20they%20lit%20up%20during%20the%20tour%20with%20no%20one%20nearby%2C%20paranormal%20activity%20could%20be%20one%20explanation%2C%20according%20to%20my%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20admit%20the%20cat%20balls%20made%20me%20feel%20more%20skeptical%20going%20into%20the%20tour%20since%20they%20seemed%20like%20a%20less%20scientific%20approach%20than%20the%20REM%20pod%20and%20EMF%20meters.%20Then%20again%2C%20as%20Compton%20reminded%20us%2C%20there's%20no%20proof%20for%20any%20of%20this.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20paranormal%20investigations%2C%20it's%20more%20about%20the%20experience%20and%20feeling%20of%20the%20ghost%20hunt%20than%20the%20mechanics%20of%20the%20hunt%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20we%20assembled%20in%20the%20entryway%2C%20Mungo%20began%20telling%20us%20about%20the%20Morris%20family%20and%20the%20history%20of%20the%20house.%20Then%2C%20the%20cat%20ball%20inside%20the%20Octagon%20Room%20across%20the%20hall%20went%20off.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20octagon%20room%20inside%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65143c951c099d0019ad3315%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMorris-Jumel%20Mansion.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20built%20as%20their%20summer%20home%20to%20escape%20the%20city%2C%20which%20is%20funny%20to%20think%20about%20now%2C%20but%20at%20the%20time%20the%20city%20had%20only%20reached%20...%26quot%3B%20Mungo%20paused%20as%20the%20cat%20ball%20lit%20up%20in%20the%20empty%20Octagon%20Room%2C%20where%20it%20had%20clearly%20not%20been%20touched.%20I%2C%20along%20with%20other%20members%20of%20our%20group%2C%20let%20out%20a%20nervous%20giggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInteresting.%20Well%2C%20hello%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20before%20continuing.%20%26quot%3BThe%20city%20had%20only%20reached%20about%20Canal%20Street%2C%20so%20this%20up%20here%20was%20farmland.%20Before%20the%20Morrises%2C%20before%20colonization%2C%20this%20was%20the%20land%20of%20the%20Lenape%2C%20and%20this%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20unceded%20land%20of%20the%20Lenape.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20tour%20continued%20in%20the%20parlor%2C%20where%20Eliza%20Jumel%20married%20Aaron%20Burr%20in%201833.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20parlor%20at%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65143c941c099d0019ad3311%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20parlor%20at%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20paranormal-investigation%20equipment%20lit%20up%20in%20the%20parlor%2C%20but%20Compton%20said%20that%20three%20weeks%20ago%2C%20she%20walked%20into%20the%20empty%20house%20on%20a%20Sunday%20and%20heard%20the%20room's%20original%20pianoforte%20playing%20music%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20the%20dining%20room%2C%20Mungo%20pointed%20out%20a%20clock%20decorated%20with%20a%20moon%20that%20is%20said%20to%20wink%20at%20handsome%20men.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20clock%20with%20a%20face%20inside%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65143c951c099d0019ad3317%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20clock%20inside%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20visitors%20stood%20in%20front%20of%20the%20clock%2C%20but%20none%20reported%20seeing%20the%20moon%20wink%20at%20them.%20I%20didn't%20get%20a%20wink%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMungo%20said%20that%20while%20the%20dining%20room%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20one%20of%20our%20more%20active%20spaces%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20moon%20is%20known%20to%20be%20flirty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20did%20wink%20at%20me%20last%20week%2C%20so%20he%20is%20exploring%20himself%2C%26quot%3B%20Mungo%20said%2C%20eliciting%20a%20laugh%20from%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20then%20headed%20upstairs%20to%20Jumel's%20bedroom%2C%20where%20Compton%20introduced%20dowsing%20rods%2C%20another%20ghost-hunting%20tool.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karen%20Compton%20uses%20dousing%20rods%20to%20detect%20paranormal%20activity%20at%20the%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651494d7eee46600193bb272%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKaren%20Compton%20uses%20dousing%20rods%20to%20detect%20paranormal%20activity%20at%20the%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDowsing%20rods%20have%20historically%20been%20used%20to%20locate%20underground%20water%20sources%2C%20Compton%20said.%20The%20L-shaped%20tools%20feature%20long%20sticks%20that%20swing%20from%20side%20to%20side%2C%20even%20when%20held%20still%20by%20their%20handles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20is%20that%20if%20they%20cross%2C%20then%20you've%20found%20a%20spirit%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWould%20anybody%20like%20to%20try%20them%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20volunteered.%20I%20tried%20to%20stay%20perfectly%20still%2C%20but%20I%20could%20feel%20the%20way%20the%20slightest%20movement%20would%20cause%20the%20rods%20to%20swing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEliza%2C%20are%20you%20here%3F%26quot%3B%20Compton%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20seconds%2C%20the%20rods%20crossed.%20I%20wasn't%20convinced%20that%20a%20ghost%20had%20caused%20the%20movement%2C%20but%20I%20was%20excited%20that%20%3Cem%3Esomething%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20handed%20them%20to%20another%20member%20of%20the%20group%2C%20and%20the%20rods%20pointed%20towards%20a%20lamp%20in%20the%20corner%20of%20the%20room.%20Compton%20explained%20that%20everything%20in%20the%20room%20was%20original%20except%20for%20the%20carpeting%20and%20that%20lamp.%20The%20original%20fixture%20shattered%20during%20the%20installation%20of%20new%20carpet%2C%20which%20some%20interpreted%20as%20Jumel%20expressing%20her%20displeasure%20at%20the%20design%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20you%20like%20the%20carpet%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20someone%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rods%20remained%20still.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20parlor%20that%20served%20as%20George%20Washington's%20war%20room%20in%201776%20seemed%20particularly%20active%20as%20Compton%20told%20us%20about%20his%20valet%2C%20an%20enslaved%20man%20named%20William%20%26quot%3BBilly%26quot%3B%20Lee.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223408%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20EMF%20meter%20lights%20up%20on%20a%20ghost%20tour%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651495bc1c099d0019ad4f81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222556%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20EMF%20meter%20lit%20up%20in%20George%20Washington's%20War%20Room.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people's%20EMF%20meters%2C%20including%20my%20own%2C%20flashed%20yellow%2C%20orange%2C%20and%20red%2C%20as%20Compton%20explained%20that%20Lee%20was%20a%20constant%20presence%20at%20Washington's%20side%20for%20two%20decades%20and%20was%20the%20only%20enslaved%20person%20freed%20in%20his%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20excited%20to%20hear%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20member%20of%20our%20group%20said%20of%20Lee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWilliam%20Lee%20always%20responds%2C%26quot%3B%20Compton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDid%20the%20presence%20of%20electromagnetic%20energy%20indicate%20the%20ghost%20of%20Lee%3F%20Were%20all%20the%20EMF%20meters%20in%20the%20small%20space%20simply%20activating%20each%20other%3F%20Perhaps%20my%20EMF%20meter%20was%20responding%20to%20the%20electric%20candlesticks%20placed%20on%20the%20windowsills%20to%20fill%20the%20room%20with%20a%20flickering%20yellow%20glow.%20I%20don't%20know%20enough%20about%20how%20the%20devices%20work%20to%20say%2C%20but%20I%20did%20appreciate%20the%20acknowledgement%20of%20Washington's%20complicated%20history%20as%20a%20slave%20owner%20as%20part%20of%20the%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EShe%20said%20Aaron%20Burr's%20bedchamber%2C%20where%20Lin-Manuel%20Miranda%20spent%20time%20writing%20%26quot%3BHamilton%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20featured%20a%20paranormal%20peculiarity%20known%20as%20EVP%2C%20or%20electronic%20voice%20phenomena.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aaron%20Burr's%20room%20at%20the%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65143e6a1c099d0019ad33b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAaron%20Burr's%20room%20at%20the%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20paranormal%20investigations%2C%20EVP%20is%20defined%20as%20%26quot%3Bapparent%20ghost%20voices%20attempting%20to%20communicate%20through%20typical%20audio%20recording%20equipment%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%202022%20study%20about%20paranormal%20experiences%20and%20sensory-processing%20sensitivity%20published%20in%20the%20scientific%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC9473424%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPLOS%20ONE%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthors%20Jess%20M.%20Williams%20and%20Mark%20Blagrove%20wrote%20that%20EVP%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20example%20of%20an%20illusion%20that%20results%20in%20the%20perception%20of%20meaningful%20patterns%20in%20meaningless%20stimuli%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20pareidolia%2C%20occurring%20in%20both%20visual%20and%20auditory%20forms%2C%20such%20as%20seeing%20faces%20in%20clouds%20or%20hearing%20phantom%20words%20in%20white%20noise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompton%20showed%20us%20a%20video%20taken%20in%20the%20room%20around%20seven%20years%20ago%20during%20a%20ghost%20tour%20like%20ours.%20It%20took%20a%20few%20listens%2C%20but%20I%20could%20make%20out%20what%20sounded%20like%20a%20scratchy%2C%20high-pitched%20voice%20exclaiming%20something%20unintelligible.%20It%20just%20as%20easily%20could%20have%20been%20a%20creaky%20piece%20of%20furniture%2C%20or%20distortion%20caused%20by%20overlapping%20voices%20in%20the%20recording.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDownstairs%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20we%20tried%20some%20more%20EVP%20by%20recording%20ourselves%20asking%20questions%20to%20the%20home's%20former%20residents%20and%20listening%20back%20to%20see%20if%20we%20got%20any%20response.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65143e6beee46600193b95fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20the%20ghost%20of%20Burr%20what%20he%20thought%20of%20his%20portrayal%20in%20the%20musical%20%26quot%3BHamilton%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20unfortunately%20did%20not%20get%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMungo%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20people%20who%20would%20have%20worked%20in%20the%20kitchen%20%E2%80%94%20the%20enslaved%20individuals%20whose%20names%20and%20stories%20were%20never%20recorded%20%E2%80%94%20and%20asked%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20come%20forward.%20The%20REM%20pod%20and%20recordings%20remained%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20still%20didn't%20believe%20in%20ghosts%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tour%2C%20but%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20or%20hear%20one%20during%20my%20visit.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20outside%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68ed1afacc993f9955d01267%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20outside%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20a%20skeptic%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20hoping%20to%20hear%20some%20mysterious%20footsteps%20or%20feel%20a%20sudden%20chill.%20This%20made%20me%20hyper-aware%20of%20every%20aspect%20of%20my%20surroundings%2C%20which%20caused%20some%20false%20alarms%2C%20like%20a%20mysterious%20shadow%20that%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20my%20own%20reflection%20in%20a%20glass%20barrier.%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20interpret%20anything%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20paranormal%20activity%20if%20you%20want%20to%20find%20it%20badly%20enough%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20really%20believe%20in%20it%20to%20begin%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20learning%20about%20the%20way%20paranormal%20investigations%20are%20conducted%20and%20getting%20to%20try%20out%20some%20of%20the%20equipment%2C%20which%20I%20never%20would%20have%20known%20about%20or%20bought%20myself.%20I%20also%20appreciated%20that%20the%20tour%20welcomed%20skeptics%20and%20simply%20presented%20stories%20and%20theories%20without%20trying%20to%20convince%20anyone%20of%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMungo%20said%2C%20more%20than%20anything%2C%20the%20goal%20of%20the%20tours%20is%20to%20educate%20visitors%20about%20the%20mansion's%20history%20and%20its%20extraordinary%20occupants.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65143f7aeee46600193b963e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMorris-Jumel%20Mansion.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Morris-Jumel%20Mansion%20didn't%20always%20embrace%20its%20reputation%20as%20a%20haunted%20building%2C%20but%20Mungo%20said%20the%20museum%20started%20offering%20ghost%20tours%20and%20paranormal%20investigations%20about%20a%20decade%20ago%20to%20help%20bring%20more%20visitors%20to%20the%20little-known%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20kind%20of%20a%20hidden%20gem%2C%20and%20because%20this%20is%20a%20fun%20thing%20that%20has%20a%20different%20audience%20than%20museums%20tend%20to%20have%2C%20it's%20a%20gateway%20for%20them%20to%20come%20and%20see%20this%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Mungo%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20do%20still%20get%20the%20history%20of%20the%20house.%20We%20do%20sneak%20it%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20or%20not%20Jumel's%20ghost%20haunts%20the%20property%2C%20Mungo%20feels%20that%20her%20story%20is%20worth%20telling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEliza%20Jumel%20is%20the%20coolest%20lady%20in%20American%20history%20and%20we%20completely%20forgot%20about%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20only%20place%20that's%20still%20talking%20about%20her.%20It's%20layers%20upon%20layers%20of%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20This%20story%20was%20published%20in%20September%202023%20and%20updated%20in%20October%202025.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhaunted-places-historic-homes-to-visit-ghost-tour-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%