tors%20to%20integrate%20the%20sophisticated%20systems%20and%20their%20computerized%20displays%20and%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20projects%20face%20an%20inherent%20strain%3A%20They%20must%20be%20built%20rapidly%20enough%20for%20current%20missions%20but%20with%20sufficient%20capability%20to%20remain%20effective%20in%20a%20war%20that%20could%20be%20decades%20into%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20lengthy%20process%20that%20has%20been%20consolidated%20to%20a%20smaller%20number%20of%20major%20companies%20since%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Cold%20War.%20And%20it%20is%20this%20system%20that%20the%20Defense%20Department%20wants%20to%20widen%20to%20new%20players%20and%20speed%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESilicon%20Valley%20titans%2C%20who%20specialize%20in%20rushing%20new%20digital%20services%20to%20the%20market%2C%20have%20also%20criticized%20the%20defense%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Pentagon%20recently%20failed%20its%20seventh%20consecutive%20audit%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20agency's%20leadership%20has%20little%20idea%20how%20its%20annual%20budget%20of%20more%20than%20%24800%20billion%20is%20spent%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20an%20op-ed%20he%20cowrote%20with%20biotech%20entrepreneur%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20for%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20and%20Ramaswamy%20wrote%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20op-ed%20as%20co-leaders%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-thanks-trump-stepping-back-doge-politics-white-house-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20White%20House%20DOGE%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ramaswamy%20left%20DOGE%20in%20January%2C%20and%20Musk%20left%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a1a0914-8502-4b2c-bc71-c5faa7f2ea5c%5C%22%3EPrimes%20can%20move%20slowly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20some%20major%20weapons%20develo