tive%20continues%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20that%20single%20pilot%2C%20the%20project%20has%20spread%20like%20the%20roots%20of%20a%20forest%2C%20reaching%20over%201%2C600%20villages%20with%20more%20than%20three%20million%20native%20trees%20planted.%20The%20model%20is%20as%20much%20social%20as%20it%20is%20environmental.%20TBTP%20stresses%20not%20only%20planting%20but%20also%20long-term%20care.%20Saplings%20are%20nurtured%20for%20up%20to%2030%20months%2C%20creating%20steady%20employment%20for%20local%20residents%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20women%20and%20youth%2C%20who%20make%20up%2070%25%20of%20the%20caregiving%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20happens%20after%20planting%3F%20The%20work%20that%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlanting%20is%20only%20the%20start.%20The%20real%20effort%20is%20in%20the%20care%20%E2%80%94%20watering%2C%20pruning%2C%20and%20protecting%20%E2%80%94%20until%20the%20trees%20can%20stand%20on%20their%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%20Gurpreet%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEmpowering%20youth%20through%20this%20work%20is%20important.%20It%20is%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F467221%2Freeva-sood-chemical-free-farming-empower-rural-women-agriva-naturally%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstilling%20purpose%2C%20building%20self-reliance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20reshaping%20how%20communities%20view%20their%20future.%20When%20young%20people%20become%20guardians%20of%20these%20forests%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20protect%20the%20environment%2C%20they%20lead%20their%20communities%20towards%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Inderjit%20and%20many%20others%2C%20this%20change%20has%20become%20deeply%20personal.%20A%20seasoned%20cultivator%2C%20he%20had%20long%20watched%20his%20soil%20decline.%20He%20offered%20a%20kanal%20of%20his%20private%20land%20to%20the%20project%20with%20cautious